text: SRY is the HUGO Gene Nomenclature Committee assigned symbol for the mammalian gene "sex determining region Y". SRY is an abbreviation that can also mean: * Southern Railway of British Columbia * Shoeburyness railway station (National Rail station code SRY) * Surrey (Chapman code SRY and ISO 3166-2:GB geocode GB-SRY) * Dasht-e Naz Airport IATA code * "Sorry" (see Suffering), as a slang abbreviation for an expression of sympathy for another's suffering
title: SRY (disambiguation)
